Package com.agenarisk.api.model

Class CalculationResult

java.lang.Object
com.agenarisk.api.model.CalculationResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
Storable
public class CalculationResult extends Object implements Storable
CalculationResult class represents a view of the Node's calculation results.
It is valid at the time of retrieval and is not maintained.
Author:
Eugene Dementiev
